Greetings all,

I Have created a new map for all our enjoyment. This map, FY_Fenced_In_06, is a Counter-Strike: Source map created with fog, wind and a 3D Skybox to create a level of realism never before felt by counter-Strike: Source players.


To install this map copy the "FY_Fenced_In_06.bsp" AND the "FY_Fenced_In_06.txt" files to your "Counter-Strike: Source\cstrike\maps" directory.

I hope you all have a great time playing Counter-Strike: Source.
->Kr4m3r


To contact me for help, comment, or bugs, Email me at Lead.and.medals@gmail.com
